WHAT IS IT?
-----------

  'Noblik' is a Workbench game in which you move diagonal bars,
and the more bars you move, the more points you get. As you might
guess, there is one catch: do not 'connect' bars together or, in
other words, do not move a bar so the end of that bar 'touch' the
end of another bar... if that happens, both bars will explode and
the game will be over.

  Have fun!

